    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onions are caramelising, top, tail, peel and grate the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Trim the<strong> spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> then slice widthways into quarters</p><p>Chop each quarter into 4 lengthways – these are your<strong> shredded spring onions</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
